OL,6,FThe top three reasons for presenting
OL,7,Fas homeless were accommodation not
OL,8,Fbeing reasonable, sharing breakdown/
OL,9,Ffamily dispute, and loss of rented
OL,10,Faccommodation.
OL,12,FMr Lyons announced the new funding
OL,13,Fduring a debate on Homelessness
OL,14,FAwareness Week in Stormont on Monday.
