OL,3,CCommunities minister pledges #6.7
OL,4,Cmillion for homelessness prevention
OL,6,FHe told MLAs: "Firstly, following
OL,7,FOctober monitoring, I am providing an
OL,8,Fadditional #6.7 million pounds for the
OL,9,FHousing Executive to prevent the risk
OL,10,Fof homelessness service closures and
OL,11,Fensure that its statutory obligations
OL,12,Fcan continue to be met.
OL,14,F"Secondly, many of our homelessness
OL,15,Fservice providers have been operating
OL,16,Fon a month-to-month funding model,
OL,17,Fwhich has created too much uncertainty
OL,18,Ffor this critical work that changes
OL,19,Fnow. Today I can announce that this
OL,20,Ffunding will be confirmed until the
OL,21,Fend of the year.
OL,26,@nD@OOUvD@AOU
