OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F446A1733234945
OL,3,CCommunities minister pledges #6.7
OL,4,Cmillion for homelessness prevention
OL,6,F"And finally, I'm also pleased to
OL,7,Fannounce that for the financial year
OL,8,F2025/2026 and moving forward, the
OL,9,FNorthern Ireland Housing Executive,
OL,10,Ffor the first time ever, will have
OL,11,Ftheir own specific funding allocation
OL,12,Ffor homelessness prevention.
OL,14,F"The voluntary and community sector
OL,15,Fdeserves this clarity, and I am sure
OL,16,Fmembers today will welcome this
OL,17,Fpositive step in the right direction.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU
