OL,3,CCommunities minister pledges #6.7
OL,4,Cmillion for homelessness prevention
OL,6,F"We have to make the strategic shift
OL,7,Fto the prevention of homelessness.
OL,8,FThat is what I have said for some
OL,9,Ftime. That remains my ambition, and
OL,10,Fthe proposals that I have outlined
OL,11,Ftoday show my commitment to that."
OL,13,FMr Lyons earlier stated that he would
OL,14,Fbe bringing a housing supply strategy
OL,15,Fto the Executive "in the coming days".
OL,17,FHe said: "The new strategy will
OL,18,Fprovide a long-term framework for the
OL,19,Factions required to increase supply
OL,20,Fand address the main barriers to
OL,21,Fprogress.
