OL,3,CCommunities minister pledges #6.7
OL,4,Cmillion for homelessness prevention
OL,6,F"It recognises that transforming
OL,7,Fhousing supply will require not only a
OL,8,Fcollective response from the Executive
OL,9,Fbut real collaboration that includes
OL,10,Flocal government, community groups,
OL,11,Fthe construction industry and
OL,12,Ffinancial bodies, and I will have a
OL,13,Fmajor announcement to make alongside
OL,14,Fthis in the coming weeks.
OL,16,F"Increasing the range of affordable
OL,17,Fhousing options is key to the
OL,18,Fprevention of homelessness."
