OL,6,FMr Lyons added: "I just want to
OL,7,Fclarify that it's my intention that
OL,8,Fwill not be just for 25/26 but moving
OL,9,Fforward, because I think we need to
OL,10,Finvest far more in homelessness
OL,11,Fprevention.
OL,13,F"We need to do the other things as
OL,14,Fwell, but we need to do that now, and
OL,15,Fthat needs to continue and I want that
OL,16,Fto be not just this year, but every
OL,17,Fyear."
